headline: Quanta Services (PWR) Earnings Surge 23%, Reinforcing Bullish Growth Narratives
summary: Quanta Services (PWR) posted a standout year, delivering earnings growth of 23%, well ahead of its 5-year average of 18.1% per year. With earnings expected to rise at 17.83% annually and revenue set to grow 11.1% per year, the business is forecasting gains that outpace the broader US market. Margins ticked slightly higher to 3.7%, underscoring the company’s continued profitability momentum. See our full analysis for Quanta Services.
